    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "####<i class=\"fa-duotone fa-regular fa-file-music\"></i> Step 2: Define the function\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Add <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-drum\" style=\"color: #E565F5; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Beat </span> and <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-boombox\" style=\"color: #58BEF9; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Bass </span> sounds to define the [beat](#clickable=id:thebeat) function.\r\n2. Press Run. Notice how the beat repeats!\r\n\r\n[<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb-on\"></i> Hint](#clickable=flyout-id:play---id-up-inside:hint_block)\r\n\r\n---\r\n*Example timeline:*\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/1fcec58260addb806ab12a9d3af86304-image-1744664200641.png)",
